title: Striploin Steak Carne Asada Tacos with Avocado Pico de Gallo and Tortilla Chips
description: Garlic-marinated steak crusted with Enchilada spices packs these taco with flavour. Wrapped in warm tortillas and topped with smoky chipotle sauce and tomato-avocado salsa, there's nothing better...except having some extra salsa and chips on the side!
